title: Seth Meyers Interviews SNL Writer Julio Torres (Podcast Exclusive)
description:
On today's episode, Seth interviews writer/comedian Julio Torres about working at Saturday Night Live. They discuss how Julio got from El Salvador to the SNL writers' room, and dig deep into the inspiration behind some of his most notable sketches like Wells For Boys and The Sink.
Then, you'll hear Julio's recent stand-up set from his appearance on Late Night.
